&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Prospect to build and maintain a healthy pipeline&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Identify and secure opportunities with prototyping, ramp, production and long-term, strategic manufacturing contracts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
