&lt;li&gt;Understand and verify operations of the mechanical, electrical, and software components of the entire automated system, including PLC’s, motors, sensors, pick-to-light systems, conveyors, mechanical components, and computer interfaces&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Train team in the operation and maintenance of all MHE and related software&lt;/li&gt;
