&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About MISUMI Americas&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;MISUMI Americas, a division of MISUMI Group, is a leading provider of standard, configurable, and custom manufacturing solutions. By integrating a vast catalog of components with a world-class digital manufacturing platform, MISUMI Americas empowers engineers and procurement teams to accelerate innovation across the entire product lifecycle. With operations in the San Francisco Bay Area and Chicago, the company serves as a vital partner for the most innovative companies in the Americas.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Impact In This Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;As the Director of Product Management, you will own the product strategy and integrated roadmap across multiple product domains at MISUMI Americas, including catalog platform and search, e-commerce platform experience, supply chain, customer experience, and business systems. You will champion a significant product organization, directing both senior individual contributors and people managers to translate high-level company strategy into actionable, impact-driven roadmaps that deliver measurable results.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Serving as the vital link between executive leadership, Engineering, Design, Operations, and Go-To-Market teams, you ensure we are solving the most critical problems with increasing speed and precision. You will operate as both a visionary leader and a hands-on navigator, establishing clear direction while actively resolving trade-offs and elevating the standard of excellence across our expanding product management organization.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
